## 2                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             Phuket to Chiang Mai with AirAsia. Worst service I have ever experienced on an aircraft. I'm 6'4" tall and literally could not sit in my seat without physically bruising my knees as the legroom is that short. I stood for entire flight apart from when seatbelt signs were on and came away with bad bruising to both my knees. Despite there being 11 extra legroom seats available the cabin crew would not let me sit there (even for extra payment that I offered) but instead just smiled at me as I stood. I showed then the damage the seat had done to my knees after take off and they just did not care. I watched them throw a lady out of the extra legroom seat who was trying to breastfeed a baby, this is how uncaring they are. On making a subsequent complaint I received a totally inadequate reply from them. If you are over 5'8" do not use. I am now looking at taking legal action for my injuries and suffering as only way I can see these airlines learning.
## 3                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Kuala Lumpur to Johor Bahru.        subtitle = paste("Total Counts: Very Negative =", sentiment_counts["1) very negative"],
                        "| Negative =", sentiment_counts["2) negative"],
                        "| Neutral =", sentiment_counts["3) neutral"],
                        "| Positive =", sentiment_counts["4) positive"],
                        "| Very Positive =", sentiment_counts["5) very positive"])) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("1) very negative" = "darkred", 
                               "2) negative" = "red", 
                               "3) neutral" = "yellow",
                               "4) positive" = "lightgreen", 
                               "5) very positive" = "darkgreen")) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 150, 25)) +
  theme_minimal()
